<p>Match each <code>patrol_type</code> to its behaviour.</p>
<pre><code>1. &quot;horizontal&quot;   2. &quot;vertical&quot;   3. &quot;chase&quot;
</code></pre>
<pre><code>A. moves up and down between two heights
B. follows the player when nearby
C. walks left and right between two x positions
</code></pre>
<p><strong>1 → ___  2 → ___  3 → ___</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

