<pre><code class="language-python">def update(self):
    if self.patrol_type == &quot;chase&quot;:
        if self.rect.x &lt; player_rect.x:
            self.rect.x += 1
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> <code>player_rect</code> must be passed in, with a safe default, and used only when it exists.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
