<p><strong>Bug C</strong> — Dead particles should be removed so the explosion fades. Right now they pile up and slow the game down.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">for exp in explosions:
    exp.update()
    exp.draw(screen)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> when an explosion <code>is_done()</code>, take it out of the list. Loop over a copy while removing.</p>
